{"tid":56602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩支那山賊　九龍鷹巢山劫行山客　七分鐘五人被搶","createTime":"2016-12-27T11:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T12:17:59.000Z","uid":35519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13ca7c60c366932d3bd0948aa47877c18726bcd7","tid":56602,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:02:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【山賊出沒．有片】<br />\n兩操國語匪鷹巢山劫行山客<br />\n七分鐘五人被搶</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/326931/xlarge/5d0bb8e2a4c8bca8002c10e65d1e4303.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F326931%2Fxlarge%2F5d0bb8e2a4c8bca8002c10e65d1e4303.jpg&h=1097b050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半百PTU上山搜捕兩名山賊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sAkTc20Dz5c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsAkTc20Dz5c&d=nDg5AbBySp3qGS%2FW34J3tnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1cd3750c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sAkTc20Dz5c</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行山旺季適逢假日，山賊出沒注意！長沙灣山徑驚現山賊行劫，最少五名行山客受害。位於長沙灣山上的鷹巢山自然教育徑，下午12時40分一名約60歲女子報稱於鄰近山路遇劫，一名男賊亮出生果刀，劫去女子一部手提電話及數十元現金，女子手部受輕傷；而於12時47分再有市民報案，一母親帶同3名子女行山時同樣於教育徑遇劫，母親及1名女兒被劫去兩部手提電話及逾千元現金。現場消息指，兩名男賊均操國語，一人身穿白衣及藍色褲，另一人穿黑衣黑褲，有途經市民目睹其中一男子落荒而逃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>警犬出動　半百PTU搜山</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查及派出機動部隊上山搜索，並向受害數名事主落口供，初步懷疑案件為同一幫人所為，兩名賊人分別作案。該山路四通八達，可通往黃大仙、沙田等地。警方沿途呼籲行山客儘量避免行走涉事路線，行山客張伯稱平日不少行山人士會選擇涉事山路遠足，認為山賊今次犯案十分猖獗，但自己無特別防範措施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/326810/xlarge/258be4a6d9962b202685ae0393b75422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F326810%2Fxlarge%2F258be4a6d9962b202685ae0393b75422.jpg&h=cdf4c167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受害行山客由警員帶走助查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/326856/xlarge/1519f9e6bbb2db3aa6b683bdf4a8b7ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F326856%2Fxlarge%2F1519f9e6bbb2db3aa6b683bdf4a8b7ff.jpg&h=94cbec06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n約60歲女事主被劫去一部手提電話及數十元現金，手部受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/326812/xlarge/5358dcd2d25426c2dd13448fea1f0a12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F326812%2Fxlarge%2F5358dcd2d25426c2dd13448fea1f0a12.jpg&h=e0031168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方派出機動部隊上山搜索。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/326834/xlarge/aa3e5989f58ead47f9a405b98db5816f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F326834%2Fxlarge%2Faa3e5989f58ead47f9a405b98db5816f.jpg&h=24bd691f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位於長沙灣山上的鷹巢山自然教育徑出現山賊，7分鐘內5人遇劫。（陳惠嫻攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/sns/article/62408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F62408&d=nDg5AbBySp3qGS%2FW34J3tnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=40767a6c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/sns/article/62408</a>"},{"pid":"46ca61795bdc16f3f6b69175b9aa8145dc8852f3","tid":56602,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:04:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd773c141c5fd777a5f55c61e43cbee63594b605","tid":56602,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鄰國專才"},{"pid":"5f7639d2ffb7fbb02883f386d4d6118f834168e4","tid":56602,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/138269_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F138269_WM.jpg&h=29daca1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0420dac03b0186a27351cf8927e5f07c4fcef171","tid":56602,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:16:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53b30b2d90aa9199991a73b56920bec8aadf170b","tid":56602,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"行個山都要驚俾人打劫<br />\n仲要唔似係II做！"},{"pid":"e0293f5c474cd6dcd61cc55214c9940c8f696cc6","tid":56602,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:29:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老味5，6段都有人老笠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸人唔係好撚富貴咩？"},{"pid":"c024442bc93c06817007659bfa299ad4c79976a2","tid":56602,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行個山都要驚俾人打劫<br />\n仲要唔似係II做！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行山不嬲要帶刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a634a2e6b3b041d460ca6225aed8e5a0c396d448","tid":56602,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"搜咩撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐車返左大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1123fdfb454bca23b89fb3580cad06236ea6b90e","tid":56602,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行山帶得幾多錢喺身"},{"pid":"262b404e3e2635423a1afd073af211f0508a8e31","tid":56602,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"收皮啦黑警<br />\nD細路企o係度俾你打就叻<br />\n你邊會捉到支那匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}